1.Minimum Viable Features (MVFs)
--------------------------------
--Functional Features:
User can create an account
User can create a pet (detailed profile)
User can create a family group (group of users + schedule)
Family group can be created for different types of events (food, medications, washing, vet appointments)

--Non-Functional Features:
Usable UI (application of UCD concepts)

2.Extended Viable Features (EVFs)
---------------------------------
Calendar View
User can create an item (food/medication/other)
Notifications (may be changed to a EVFs based off research)
Trending height and weight
